=== Noun ===
'''Résumé'''
# A document that enumerates the job related accomplishments that one has accomplished. When available, date ranges are given for everything listed. Typically requested by an employer as a means of evaluating a candidate for an open position. Usually kept as succinct as possible; often 1 page long. Convention requires that a [[cover sheet]] be attached. The job related accomplishments listed may include: High School / College education level, Previous work experience, Awards and Major accomplishments.

